	dprr:hasNoteText "Proconsul of Asia (IGRP 4.196). At the insistence of Verres (see below, Legates), he carried through the trial of Philodamus of Lampsacus (Cic. Verr. 2.1.71-76 and 83, of. 50; Ps.-Ascon. 236, 242f. Stangl; Schol. Gron. 345 Stangl)." ;
